1
00:00:47,214 --> 00:00:48,716
[ Down-tempo music plays ]

2
00:01:09,169 --> 00:01:11,171
How much longer
till we go home?

3
00:01:11,204 --> 00:01:13,708
Captain decides
when we go home!

4
00:01:15,643 --> 00:01:17,177
Can you go ask him?

5
00:01:18,312 --> 00:01:20,113
Jesus Christ!

6
00:01:20,147 --> 00:01:22,517
No one's gonna ask the captain
what time they can go home!

7
00:01:22,550 --> 00:01:23,518
Got it, kid?

8
00:01:23,551 --> 00:01:25,152
Jesus.

9
00:01:25,185 --> 00:01:26,688
Empty.

10
00:01:26,721 --> 00:01:28,723
Got to soak them again, Cap!

11
00:01:28,756 --> 00:01:31,224
Gonna be a long one tonight,
boys.

12
00:01:34,662 --> 00:01:37,431
[ Energy resonates ]

13
00:01:38,633 --> 00:01:40,467
Mother of Jesus.

14
00:01:41,569 --> 00:01:43,738
-What the fuck?
-Jesus, Mary, and Joseph.

15
00:01:43,771 --> 00:01:45,673
What the fuck's that?

16
00:01:45,707 --> 00:01:48,275
Get the fuck down!

17
00:01:49,877 --> 00:01:51,546
Fuck!

18
00:01:54,281 --> 00:01:55,717
You boys all right?

19
00:01:55,750 --> 00:01:58,586
What the fuck was that?!

20
00:01:58,620 --> 00:02:00,521
I don't know.

21
00:02:00,555 --> 00:02:02,456
[ Dramatic music plays ]

22
00:02:06,628 --> 00:02:08,563
What do you think it is?

23
00:02:08,596 --> 00:02:10,632
I don't think it's a plane.

24
00:02:10,665 --> 00:02:13,835
I don't think
we should be here.

25
00:02:13,868 --> 00:02:16,804
Boys, we're -- we're getting
out of here.

26
00:02:16,838 --> 00:02:18,271
[ Underwater bellowing ]

27
00:02:18,305 --> 00:02:20,374
-MAN: Aaah!
-Bruce!

28
00:02:20,407 --> 00:02:21,643
Bruce!

29
00:02:21,676 --> 00:02:23,143
Bruce!

30
00:02:24,879 --> 00:02:26,881
Bruce!

31
00:02:26,914 --> 00:02:28,215
Bruce!

32
00:02:28,916 --> 00:02:30,585
-Bruce!
-[ Water sloshes ]

33
00:02:30,618 --> 00:02:32,654
Aah!

34
00:02:32,687 --> 00:02:34,221
CAPTAIN: Jimmy!

35
00:02:34,254 --> 00:02:35,422
Jimmy!

36
00:02:36,958 --> 00:02:38,492
J-Jimmy!

37
00:02:40,728 --> 00:02:42,630
J-Jimmy?

38
00:02:42,664 --> 00:02:43,798
Jim?

39
00:02:44,899 --> 00:02:47,568
Who's out there?!

40
00:02:47,602 --> 00:02:50,470
[ Creature growling ]

41
00:02:50,505 --> 00:02:52,406
[ Water splashes ]

42
00:02:58,846 --> 00:03:00,414
[ Up-tempo rock music plays ]

43
00:03:00,447 --> 00:03:02,684
GARY:
There's Dinos dead ahead!

44
00:03:05,787 --> 00:03:10,223
Fire the laser cannon!

45
00:03:12,459 --> 00:03:15,362
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

46
00:03:16,998 --> 00:03:18,900
[ Coughing ]

47
00:03:18,933 --> 00:03:20,635
There's Dinos dead ahead.

48
00:03:20,668 --> 00:03:23,403
-Let's teach them how to die.
-You'll die this time!

49
00:03:25,907 --> 00:03:28,643
This Dino spine is mine!

50
00:03:28,676 --> 00:03:32,814
Aaaaah!

51
00:03:32,847 --> 00:03:34,549
Let's go berserk!

52
00:03:34,582 --> 00:03:38,753
Yeah!

53
00:03:39,721 --> 00:03:42,657
GARY:
Your Dino treachery ends here!

54
00:03:45,026 --> 00:03:46,460
No! No!

55
00:03:47,695 --> 00:03:49,229
[ Grunting ]

56
00:03:51,699 --> 00:03:53,400
Stop! Stop it!

57
00:03:53,433 --> 00:03:54,702
Stop! Stop!

58
00:03:54,736 --> 00:03:55,870
[ Electricity crackling ]

59
00:03:55,903 --> 00:03:57,905
[ Grunting ]

60
00:04:00,541 --> 00:04:02,275
-[ Electricity crackling ]
-[ Screaming ]

61
00:04:04,645 --> 00:04:06,346
It's the Dino Sorcerer.

62
00:04:06,379 --> 00:04:09,684
Prepare to die,
you human fleshbags!

63
00:04:09,717 --> 00:04:11,619
-Eat him alive!
-Yeah!

64
00:04:11,652 --> 00:04:13,386
[ Chain saw buzzing ]

65
00:04:19,961 --> 00:04:21,829
Do a dropkick!

66
00:04:22,830 --> 00:04:23,998
Aaah!

67
00:04:26,100 --> 00:04:28,401
Yeah!
Ha ha!

68
00:04:29,369 --> 00:04:32,372
Your space magic
doesn't scare me.

69
00:04:32,405 --> 00:04:33,941
Then clearly
you don't understand

70
00:04:33,975 --> 00:04:36,010
