of the crystal.

71
00:04:36,043 --> 00:04:37,745
Give me the crystal!

72
00:04:37,779 --> 00:04:38,980
Never!

73
00:04:43,818 --> 00:04:46,988
You should have stayed extinct.

74
00:04:47,021 --> 00:04:49,056
DINO: Shit.

75
00:04:49,090 --> 00:04:50,858
Gary, this is stupid.

76
00:04:50,892 --> 00:04:52,093
GARY: What?
What are you talking about?

77
00:04:52,126 --> 00:04:53,995
Yeah.
What's wrong?

78
00:04:54,028 --> 00:04:56,564
This is so -- like...

79
00:04:56,597 --> 00:04:58,065
I got to shoot him in the head?
That's it?

80
00:04:58,099 --> 00:04:59,867
Why does he get a sword
and I don't?

81
00:04:59,901 --> 00:05:02,603
GARY: Well, first of all,
you have a gun, stupid.

82
00:05:02,637 --> 00:05:03,971
Guns are better than swords.

83
00:05:04,005 --> 00:05:06,607
And, two, you're a girl.
You don't use swords.

84
00:05:06,641 --> 00:05:08,843
Um, that's not true.
Girls totally use swords.

85
00:05:08,876 --> 00:05:10,077
I kick ass with a sword.

86
00:05:10,111 --> 00:05:12,445
Well, guess what.
One, I don't care.

87
00:05:12,479 --> 00:05:14,816
Two, I'm the director, so that's
just how it's going to be.

88
00:05:14,849 --> 00:05:17,552
And three, we need to get
the shot before it gets dark.

89
00:05:17,585 --> 00:05:19,754
So come on.
Let's shoot this thing.

90
00:05:19,787 --> 00:05:21,823
Okay. Action!

91
00:05:21,856 --> 00:05:24,058
You should have stayed extinct.

92
00:05:24,091 --> 00:05:25,392
[ Bottle shatters ]

93
00:05:25,425 --> 00:05:27,028
Holy shit.
Are you okay?

94
00:05:27,061 --> 00:05:28,428
Ow!
What the fuck?

95
00:05:28,461 --> 00:05:30,430
Who threw a beer bottle
at me?!

96
00:05:30,463 --> 00:05:31,966
BILLY: I did.

97
00:05:31,999 --> 00:05:33,400
You little piss trap.

98
00:05:33,433 --> 00:05:35,970
