to party.

99
00:05:36,003 --> 00:05:38,773
Oh, fucking teenagers.

100
00:05:38,806 --> 00:05:40,074
I always thought
this place was abandoned.

101
00:05:40,107 --> 00:05:41,776
-It's Billy McDougal! Run!
-Holy shit.

102
00:05:41,809 --> 00:05:42,810
[ Indistinct shouting ]

103
00:05:42,844 --> 00:05:44,078
Guys, guys!

104
00:05:47,414 --> 00:05:50,483
Are you fucking serious?
You ruined the fucking movie!

105
00:05:50,518 --> 00:05:52,620
Get out of our clubhouse,
and stop smoking in here.

106
00:05:52,653 --> 00:05:54,989
This place is a fucking dump.

107
00:05:55,022 --> 00:05:56,724
I'm gonna put this clown
to sleep.

108
00:05:56,757 --> 00:05:58,559
No, Miles, don't.

109
00:05:58,593 --> 00:06:00,161
GARY:
Yeah, kick his ass!

110
00:06:00,194 --> 00:06:02,997
Yeah, smile when I knock
your fucking mouth out.

111
00:06:03,030 --> 00:06:04,866
GARY: Get him!

112
00:06:04,899 --> 00:06:06,834
BILLY: Hey, whoa, whoa.
Oh!

113
00:06:06,868 --> 00:06:08,636
Stop!
Stop it!

114
00:06:08,669 --> 00:06:10,370
-MILES: Fuck off!
-SAM: Leave him alone.

115
00:06:11,672 --> 00:06:13,373
MILES: [ Grunting ]

116
00:06:15,676 --> 00:06:16,911
I'm serious.

117
00:06:16,944 --> 00:06:18,913
Knock it off.

118
00:06:18,946 --> 00:06:20,114
Fuck off, man.

119
00:06:20,147 --> 00:06:22,717
I said knock it off!

120
00:06:22,750 --> 00:06:23,951
Fuck, man.

121
00:06:23,985 --> 00:06:25,485
MILES: Get the fuck off me!
Jesus.

122
00:06:25,519 --> 00:06:28,522
Hey, please use
your brain next time.

123
00:06:28,556 --> 00:06:31,058
-You good, man?
-Yeah, I'm fine.

124
00:06:31,092 --> 00:06:33,594
Hey, haven't I seen you
at school before?

125
00:06:33,628 --> 00:06:35,428
Oh, come on.

126
00:06:35,462 --> 00:06:37,698
You have.

127
00:06:37,732 --> 00:06:39,033
Yeah.

128
00:06:39,066 --> 00:06:41,168
