with these losers anyway?

130
00:06:45,673 --> 00:06:49,043
Um, well, he's my brother,

131
00:06:49,076 --> 00:06:50,945
those are his friends,
and they're not losers.

132
00:06:50,978 --> 00:06:52,179
Okay?

133
00:06:52,213 --> 00:06:53,981
TRISH: Um [Chuckles]

134
00:06:54,015 --> 00:06:58,485
Why don't you have friends
your own age?

135
00:06:59,620 --> 00:07:02,455
I do.
I'm just babysitting them.

136
00:07:02,489 --> 00:07:05,026
[ Scoffs ]
Babysitting?

137
00:07:05,059 --> 00:07:06,694
You wanted to be
in our movie, didn't you?

138
00:07:07,662 --> 00:07:09,163
-[ Whispering ] Stop it.
-Why are you telling me to stop?

139
00:07:09,196 --> 00:07:11,766
